headline: Jacobs to Hold Its Fiscal First Quarter 2026 Earnings Conference Call and Webcast
summary: Jacobs (NYSE:J) plans to release its fiscal first quarter 2026 earnings results after market close on Tuesday, Feb. 3, 2026, and will host a conference call at 4:30 p.m. ET, during which management will make a presentation focusing on the company's results and operating trends.
